		<credit project="CfPBoK@https://slebok.github.io/cfpbok/"/>
		<h1>Tag <code>T2C</code>: Variability</h1>
		Product lines and families. Work that treats families of software languages as first-class: variability modelling, software/language product lines, feature models for DSLs, configurable language components, systematic derivation of language variants. If variability is achieved primarily via modular composition mechanisms, <a href="t1d.html">T1D</a> may be primary.
